### Assignment brief
GET http://localhost:8080/api/add/brief
Accept: application/json

### Quick verification run
POST http://localhost:8080/api/add/runs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "teamName": "",
  "teamMembers": [],
  "diagramType": "mermaid",
  "humanInteractionTurns": 1,
  "reviewerRounds": 1,
  "notes": "Use concise English. Leave team member names and personal contributions blank or marked as To be filled."
}

